author: eTN Global Editor
title: Air Lease Corporation leases two Boeing 737-800 aircraft to Siam Air Transport
text:
Air Lease Corporation leases two Boeing 737-800 aircraft to Siam Air Transport   
Sep 26, 2015   
LOS ANGELES, CA - Air Lease Corporation announced lease agreements with Siam Air Transport (Thailand) for two used Boeing 737-800 aircraft. These aircraft will deliver in the fourth quarter of 2015. 
“We are very pleased to announce this lease placement with Siam Air Transport, a new customer for ALC in Asia. These aircraft are a key addition to Siam Air Transport’s fleet as they continue to expand their route network in the region,” said Jie Chen, ALC’s Executive Vice President and Managing Director, Asia.
